=== X-4 air-to-air missile ===
* Primary function: short-range air-to-air missile
* Propulsion: BMW 109-448 liquid rocket motor giving thrust for 17 seconds
* Length: 
* Diameter: (maximum)
* Wingspan: 
* Launch weight: 
* Speed: 
* Warhead: fragmentation
* Range: 
* Fuzes: Kranich acoustic proximity fuze
* Guidance system: FuG 510/238 &quot;Düsseldorf/Detmold&quot; MCLOS visual guidance with wire control
* Unit cost:
* Date deployed: never

===X-7 anti-tank missile===
* Primary function: anti-tank guided missile
* Powerplant: solid rocket motor
* Length: 
* Diameter: 
* Wingspan: 
* Weight: 
* Speed: 
* Warhead: hollow charge
**Penetration: over at 30°
* Range: 
* Fuzes: impact (?)
* Guidance system: MCLOS visual guidance with wire control
* Unit cost:
* Date deployed: never

